					&lt;tbody&gt;
						&lt;tr&gt;
							&lt;td class=&quot;content&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;&gt;
								Please be advised of the following Sales Cancellations Policy, effective immediately (19th April 2007):&lt;br /&gt;
								&lt;br /&gt;
								&lt;ul&gt;
									&lt;li&gt;
										Sales cancellations can only be accepted within 14 days of purchase&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
									&lt;li&gt;
										Members wishing to cancel a sale must return all product to FusionExcel, in original condition&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
									&lt;li&gt;
										Members wishing to cancel a sale need to complete and sign our Refund Request Form&lt;br /&gt;
										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
									&lt;li&gt;
										Please allow a minimum of 5 working days for Management to process the sales cancellation.&lt;br /&gt;
										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
									&lt;li&gt;
										Members are PROHIBITED from using the Sales Cancellation Policy to cancel sales for the intent of changing network structure or to otherwise manipulate bonus calculation.&lt;/li&gt;
								&lt;/ul&gt;
							&lt;/td&gt;
						&lt;/tr&gt;
